main event: Multiple unidentified objects were sighted by ground radar in Milwaukee, Wisconsin on June 5, 1963.
interesting points: The objects were sighted in Sector 61 and reported to the military.
The size of the objects was described as 'Multiple'.
The objects were observed traveling in a northwesterly direction.
The report states that there was 'Insufficient data' and that a report containing concluding information was also filed.
